snippet.title: Amber Heard dazzles in Isharya Jewelry Goddess Earrings in Esquire Mexico
snippet.description:
Amber Heard video: here she covers the March issue of Esquire Mexico. In the shoot, she channels a 40s pin-up girl, and wears Isharya's decadent Black Jasper Goddess Fringe Three Stone Earrings. 

Photographer: John Russo
Stylist: Ricky Bennick
Hair Stylist: Rob Talty
Make-Up Artist: Katey Denno
